    {
      "start": 512.62,
      "end": 512.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.91,
      "end": 516.61,
      "text": "I was three years old when your mother died."
    },
    {
      "start": 516.99,
      "end": 519.91,
      "text": "And you and I are almost the same age."
    },
    {
      "start": 519.91,
      "end": 523.69,
      "text": "Oh, I was three years old when your mother died."
    },
    {
      "start": 524.17,
      "end": 525.51,
      "text": "나는 세 살이었어."
    },
    {
      "start": 525.79,
      "end": 527.47,
      "text": "너의 어머니가 돌아가셨을 때."
    },
    {
      "start": 527.95,
      "end": 531.21,
      "text": "And you and I are almost the same age."
    },
    {
      "start": 531.75,
      "end": 534.49,
      "text": "너랑 나 나이가 거의 비슷했어."
    },
    {
      "start": 534.73,
      "end": 535.19,
