    {
      "start": 544.82,
      "end": 547.5,
      "text": "And she's, you know, talking about that."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.17,
      "end": 550.87,
      "text": "Was this my mother's room?"
    },
    {
      "start": 551.09,
      "end": 552.91,
      "text": "Colin이 이렇게 질문을 하는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 553.11,
